{"tid":1595823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★經濟差？】大手客斥逾3億元再狂掃8伙匯璽","createTime":"2019-09-26T08:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T10:19:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc1cfdde0c7d947c94bc22f27a7bce8c7420686","tid":1595823,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190926/photo/bkn-20190926121535379-0926_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190926122507\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190926121535379-0926_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190926122507&h=13d748b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新盤市場屢錄大手交投。新鴻基地產(00016)旗下西南九龍匯璽III周四(26日)推出352伙進行次輪銷售，市場消息透露，A組時段共有逾30伙獲認購。當中1組大手客以公司名義連購8個大單位，料涉資逾3億港元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\">該組買家上周已斥資約2億元購入8伙，兩輪銷售共購入16伙</span>，金額料逾5億元，料須繳付30%共逾1.5億元辣稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190926/bkn-20190926121535379-0926_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190926%2Fbkn-20190926121535379-0926_00842_001.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3fc0437c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190926/bkn-20190926121535379-0926_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d899cc8b933da9a0453ddb0011b83a6c4c65498","tid":1595823,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c664541ca003afa103dd654e7dc375137f0c70","tid":1595823,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"該組買家上周已斥資約2億元購入8伙，兩輪銷售共購入16伙<br />\n<br />\n該組買家上周已斥資約2億元購入8伙，兩輪銷售共購入16伙<br />\n<br />\n該組買家上周已斥資約2億元購入8伙，兩輪銷售共購入16伙"},{"pid":"cfedeb87bf7e8e09fcc4883894e9b4c511dc32bb","tid":1595823,"uid":165891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc